{0 day11-jtw}

JavaScript-to-Wasm build pipeline for js_top_worker integration.
{!Day11_jtw.Build_tools} orchestrates end-to-end JTW processing: building tool
layers per compiler version, running per-package and per-solution
generation, and assembling the content-hashed output directory.
{!Day11_jtw.Generate} drives the three generation phases -- per-package artifact
extraction (cma.js, cmi, META), per-solution worker.js production, and
final assembly into a serving-ready directory structure. {!Day11_jtw.Tool_layer}
manages the JTW tool layer lifecycle: installing js_of_ocaml and
js_top_worker, building worker.js, and extracting stdlib CMIs per OCaml
version. {!Day11_jtw.Gen} provides pure utility functions for hashing, findlib
index generation, dynamic_cmis.json creation, and container script
generation.

Depends on {!day11-opam-build}, {!day11-container}, {!day11-doc},
{!day11-layer}, and {!day11-solver}.

